flowchart TD
    A[Choose service] --> B[Choose add-ons]
    B --> C[Filter staff]
    C --> D[Choose date]
    D --> E[Load availability]
    E --> F{Slots available?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Choose time]
    F -- No --> H[Show nearby days and alternative staff]
    H --> D
    G --> I[Review booking]
    I --> J[Confirm appointment]
    J --> K[Success]
    K --> L[Manage booking]
    L --> M[Reschedule]
    L --> N[Cancel]
